      "raw_text": "Operator Mitchell of Perma sta\nton, on the Northern Pacific, who\nwas responsible for the wreck at\nParadise Saturday in which nine\nlives were lost, will be held for\ncriminal negligence. Mitchell re-\nported No. 5. the westbound pas\nsenger, as NOT having passed Perma\nwhen it really had gone forward.\nThis caused the dispatcher at Mis-\nsoula to give the freight train or\nders to move eastward and meet\nthe passenger at Perma, hence the\nwreck\n\n\nUnder the laws of Montana\nMitchell is guilty of manslaughter,\nn these are the facts. Northern\nPacific officials here think Mitchell\nwill be prosecuted."
    }
  ]
